zm_legends:

this map is the v2 since the first version was pretty laggy and i made a total remake of it.

The map has features a big church several underground ways, enterable houses and many campspots.
Hunting is also possible, since there are many long ways.

The map runs best with about 30-50 ppl.

Have fun playing it.
